onstrue a break several of the commandment if you try i really felt dishonor by the action my daughter be only nine year old but i think she should have be old and mature enough to realize her action i have difficulty blame her directly for religiou teach her mother swear to but when i discuss thi with my daughter she make it clear she believe in buddhism and not christianity my initial response of anger moderate wa to suggest if there be no faith in christ then why do she celebrate easter or christma i suggest i would never force her to practice my religiou belief by celebrate holiday with her again i do not want to drive her from the fold and would be will to allow her to continue practice buddhism a though i have a choice see her only for two day out of fourteen but i want her to want to embrace christianity any suggestion if you have a response please e-mail me a copy i not a regular reader of thi newsgroup naturally feel free to post too thank and i hope you have a happy easter drew drew watson system analysi encore computer corp dwatson customer service 